config_meta.description:
Potenzial-Kaskade inspiriert von in-context Lernen großer Sprachmodelle.
Höhere Kopplungsgewinne betonen semantische Verstärkung, während ein
erweitertes Kohärenzfenster den langsamen Drift der Token-Kohärenz
beobachtet.

tri_layer.formal: Θ and β drift when the cascade gain couples σ(β(R-Θ)) to Mandala coherence; the null trace tracks gate/zeta deltas as the falsification baseline.
tri_layer.empirical: Synthetic potentials ramp from quiet to resonant, raising Θ by 0.705 and β by 1.945; gate delta vs. null = -0.081.
tri_layer.poetic: Steepness remembers the hymn it just sang: the membrane opens, Θ becomes the new condition, and the quiet null baseline watches dawn ignite again.
